output.analysis:
Let me analyze this post according to the required criteria:
1. Has CMF: No visible CMF number, but this doesn't automatically disqualify it as propaganda.
2. Refers to candidate: Yes, explicitly mentions "George Simion" who is position nr. 2 on the presidential candidates list.
3. Addresses wide population: Yes, this is a paid Facebook advertisement targeting a potential audience of 100,001-500,000 people, specifically in Timiș area.
4. Electoral objective: Yes, clearly has electoral intent: - Mentions distribution of posters with George Simion - Uses campaign hashtags (#VoteazăAUR) - Explicitly asks for support for bringing change - Uses campaign-specific language ("Împreună putem aduce schimbarea")
5. Journalism: No, this is clearly a campaign message, not journalistic content.
6. Personal opinion: No, this is an organized campaign message paid for by "UNIWORLD - MEDIA SRL" on behalf of AUR.
The post clearly demonstrates characteristics of electoral propaganda: - Direct candidate mention - Call for support - Campaign materials distribution - Electoral hashtags - Paid distribution

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This post constitutes electoral propaganda because: - It directly promotes presidential candidate George Simion - Involves distribution of campaign materials (posters) - Uses campaign slogans and calls for support - Is a paid advertisement reaching a wide audience - Has clear electoral intent through its messaging and hashtags
conclusion.message-for-police: UNIWORLD - MEDIA SRL și AUR, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin continuarea propagandei electorale după încheierea perioadei legale de campanie, distribuind un anunț plătit pe Facebook (ID: 3554420868191864) care promovează candidatul George Simion la președinție, după ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024. Postarea include distribuirea de afișe electorale cu candidatul, folosește hashtag-uri de campanie (#VoteazăAUR), și face apel direct la susținerea candidatului prin mesajul "Împreună putem aduce schimbarea pe care o merită România", având un evident caracter de propagandă electorală și vizând influențarea votului prin atingerea unui public țintă de până la 500.000 de persoane în regiunea Timiș.
